<SceneText>
  <FriendlyName>Chapter 1 (Asbel) - End</FriendlyName>
  <Speakers>
    <Section>Speaker</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>シェリア</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Cheria</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>29</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>アスベル</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Asbel</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>28</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>終わったのよね、これで……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's over now, isn't it...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>29</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ああ。
だがこれは始まりに過ぎない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah. But beyond this, it's just the beginning.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>２度とシュヴァルツを生み出さないように
人間は変わっていかなきゃならない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Humans need to change so that Schwartz
is never brought back into this world.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>その為の戦いの……始まりだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The battle for that purpose... is only just beginning.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>きっと厳しい戦いね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'm sure it's going to be a tough battle.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>29</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>それでもなんとかやっていけるさ。
俺にシェリアがいるように
人はみんな誰かと繋がっている</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Even so, we'll get it done somehow. Just like
I have you here for me, everyone has
someone they're connected to.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>一人では道を間違える事があっても
それを正してくれる人が側にいるのなら
きっと……大丈夫だ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Even if you go down the road path on your own,
if you have someone by your side to correct them,
I'm sure... everything will be alright.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ありがとう、シェリア。　俺を支えてくれて</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Thank you, Cheria. For supporting me.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>アスベル……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Asbel...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>29</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
